47&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7Vy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=168ecd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1439565347</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/652770334453268501/0fa3b8785cbee0c9.jpg?width=400&amp;height=207\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F652770334453268501%2F0fa3b8785cbee0c9.jpg%3Fwidth%3D400%26height%3D207&h=dfc8d8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/652770334453268503/mona.jpg?width=400&amp;height=224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F652770334453268503%2Fmona.jpg%3Fwidth%3D400%26height%3D224&h=3099d25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/653960908934217728/9.png?width=1440&amp;height=600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F653960908934217728%2F9.png%3Fwidth%3D1440%26height%3D600&h=411a9a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/651670443480186881/653960903531692032/10.png?width=400&amp;height=168\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F651670443480186881%2F653960903531692032%2F10.png%3Fwidth%3D400%26height%3D168&h=77d71a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_1.png&h=39da6548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_2.png&h=b75562ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_3.png&h=7bff6235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_4.png&h=713a6b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_5.png&h=bd906bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://another-eden.jp/special-art2/img/playback/playback_6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanother-eden.jp%2Fspecial-art2%2Fimg%2Fplayback%2Fplayback_6.png&h=331f6c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ.建唔建議首抽?<br />\nA.唔建議,因為刷一次首抽要差唔多30分鐘,要5星奶開局不如8591/淘寶<br />\n<br />\nQ.首抽抽咩好<br />\nA.5星奶-瑪莉(大獎) 或者 最新既 蝶火女 姐係紅色和服果個蘇賽特 (AS) &gt;其次水劍(謝提), 水法(麥提/AS), 巫女(尤奈) 基本上宜家有五星就練 <br />\n基本上大部分五星都有用, 不過你要最勁既就果幾隻<br />\n奶: 瑪莉 或者 火補(蘿潔塔) (補.法攻.異常盾)<br />\n物理打手: 忍者(燕) 茜AS 蝶火女 (蘇賽特, 之後有專武會用原版多) etc.<br />\n法師:水法 (麥提/AS) 之後有專武用原版都勁<br />\n輔助: 巫女(尤奈)<br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇得同人玩?<br />\nA.冇,只係一隻單機到GAME,抽到5星唔洗拎上黎曬,冇人想知<br />\n(其實都可以既 大家一齊開心. 不過唔知會唔會引起其他人暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\nQ.副本係咩黎?<br />\nA.係次元裂縫入面可以打到角色既職業書,升星書<br />\n每日0500、1100、1700、2300時會回復1張綠票1張紅票。<br />\n打完第11章,係次元就會開放HARD難度<br />\n打完第25章,係次元就會開放VERY HARD難度<br />\n<br />\n【心得】副本系統須知、天冥值介紹及角色升星(升級)職業書出處(更新國際版V2.0.2) (取自巴哈 貓友)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26snA%3D770&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7Vy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=98e7e0ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29220&amp;snA=770</a><br />\n<br />\nQ.爆左主線之後有咩做<br />\nA.百討 釣魚 外傳 礦坑 清票<br />\n<br />\nQ.過左劇情,d怪打唔返點算?<br />\nA.去次元夾縫左邊度門,有得入返去打過左既劇情<br />\n<br />\nQ.主角群洗唔洗升5星<br />\nA.升啦,男主,大波艾美,青蛙,海蕾娜,莉卡, _王 都有得上5星 (日服),係爭阿妹未有. 而邂逅角 (阿佐美, 迦琉, 思琳) 優先用夢書升5星 因為你唔會有機會抽到佢地5星"},{"pid":"5b6253a18cbe24b16b3fd88f53da3041d082520d","tid":1858263,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"Q.邊到打最多經<br />\nA.現階段國際版v2.0.2 - 魔獸城,最常出4隻<br />\n宜家出埋1.5後篇可以去魔獸城隱藏道路刷經驗<br />\n之後有封域就可以打經驗關 (1張紅票)<br />\n<br />\nQ.角色能力盤點數夠唔夠用?<br />\nA.當你最高lv時,夠你點曬佢<br />\n<br />\nQ.戰鬥相關問題<br />\nA.力量-物攻<br />\n智力-魔攻,補量<br />\n耐力-物防<br />\n精神-魔防<br />\n速度-行動順序<br />\n幸運-爆擊率 (法師法攻本身冇爆擊 升幸運聲稱可以減低被爆擊率)<br />\n<br />\nQ.有冇攻略網站推介<br />\n[url][url]A.https://<a href=\"http://games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/[/url][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.gaym.jp%2FiPhone%2Fanother-eden%2F%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7Vy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=cba88709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">games.gaym.jp/iPhone/another-eden/[/url][/url]</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/anaden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fanaden%2F&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7Vy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f6baea30\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/anaden/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FB.php%3Fbsn%3D29220%26subbsn%3D0&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7Vy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f017dbd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=29220&amp;subbsn=0</a> 巴哈<br />\n<br />\nQ.仲有冇其他野要注意?<br />\nA.除左信箱每日送20石之外,買石個到仲有廣告10石拎,總共30石<br />\n<br />\n最新版本：<br />\n同P5 合作，新手恩物<br />\n兩隻都算實用<br />\n<br />\n<im